{"tid":695814,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"硬件撚討論硬件知識、砌機LIST、解答問題集中帖(88)請睇#1卡關到2046","createTime":"2018-06-09T13:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T13:54:19.000Z","uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0fa2282937526835169015cc3b80bb6a07cd80","tid":695814,"uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:47:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">新人求List需知</span></span><br />\n<br />\n為方便連登眾巴絲可以好好幫助你，請你好好合作<br />\n不但可以令連登眾巴絲可以盡快回覆你的問題，更可以令條List更適合你所需<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">關於所有店舖事項請巴打從其他有效方式聯絡 </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">顯卡係蝗語，請講顯示卡或display card </span><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/9Li1671.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9Li1671.gif&h=e2849c04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. Budget<br />\nNO MONEY NO TALK ，預算上限寬鬆可以買好一點，預算太低可能要將就或繼續儲錢<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">打機INTEL<br />\n多工AMD</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2. 電腦主要用途<br />\n你想玩咩遊戲? (多數砌機都會打機，如果唔係請另外講明)<br />\n最好講game名，唔好一句steam game/blizzard/EA game就算<br />\n因為成千上萬隻人地唔知你玩邊隻<br />\n需唔需要直播或錄製遊戲影片?<br />\n<br />\n3. 個人需求<br />\n玩以上遊戲你最低可接受嘅畫質(Ultra/高/中/低)?最低可接受幾fps?<br />\n如果你預計會玩新遊戲，想幾耐唔駛升級電腦硬件?<br />\n想唔想超頻?散熱需求如何?使唔使靜過Dyson?<br />\n有冇特定嘅牌子信仰?想唔想有華麗嘅RGB光效?<br />\n<br />\n4. 現在或將會使用mon的類型<br />\n解像度有分1080p, 2K(1440p), 4K(2160p)<br />\n更新頻率有分60Hz, 144Hz, 240Hz<br />\n你想要咩解像度(畫質)同更新頻率(流暢度)?<br />\n解像度高，會對打機效能造成影響，但畫質會更好<br />\n更新頻率高，如效能足夠可以造成比低更新頻率更好嘅流暢度<br />\n<br />\n5. 自己都學習一些<br />\n講真，有一班巴絲好憎伸手黨，所以建議你行多一兩步<br />\n哪怕你直接照抄悠二巴打List放上黎問，佢地都會出手幫助<br />\n只是Ctrl-C和Ctrl-V咁簡單，大家都會開心嘅事點解唔做呢?<br />\n甚至可能你在過程中已經搵到需要的答案都不一定!<br />\n(悠二List網站 : <a href=\"http://yujihw.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com&d=TM1NSpFlEb2zKV9rxSrzWv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=72fe8cf5\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com</a>)<br />\n<br />\n6.  <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><del>大腦</del>Google係一樣很有用的東西</span></span><br />\n<br />\n7. 火牛冇乜所謂一般夠用： antec eco2 550w<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">邊個1001唔開post</span>"},{"pid":"9504d68ad32a5aea643233ee41861e54800e6e9e","tid":695814,"uid":81723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:48:48.000Z","msg":"自膠原來要開89先岩<br />\n開左88<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"400ce7e6b673df9b4ad9203ec2947e68f366558a","tid":695814,"uid":54942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:50:47.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"09084ae7264378114a446e55c191216fda87bc9a","tid":695814,"uid":54942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:51:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開過佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b9dea747d010c67e03904c34436226c28c05454","tid":695814,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:51:40.000Z","msg":"再開？"},{"pid":"b6905b2883540154bc3758b7722ec8aa79ed9adf","tid":695814,"uid":1123,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T13:54:19.000Z","msg":"硬件撚討論硬件知識、砌機LIST、解答問題集中帖(89)請睇#1卡關到2046<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/695822/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/695822/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}